#

Simple Roast Turkey with Garlic and Lemon

195 min
$40
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main DishHoliday Dinner

Tags:

EasyHealthyHoliday

Description

A juicy and flavorful turkey infused with the fresh taste of garlic and lemon, perfect for any gathering!

Ingredients

  • whole turkey: 1 (12-14 lbs)
  • olive oil: 1/4 cup
  • garlic cloves: 10, minced
  • lemon: 2, halved
  • fresh rosemary: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • salt: 1 tablespoon
  • black pepper: 1 teaspoon
